{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 21891,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「美樹ちゃん、逃げッ…………！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Miki-chan, run away...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21892,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………っ、うっ……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Ugh...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21893,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "無敵結界も、聖刀日光の剣さばきも意味をなさず、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Neither the invincible barrier nor the holy sword Nikkou's blade technique had any effect,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21894,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "健太郎の胴が半ばから断たれた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Kentaro's torso was severed halfway."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21895,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「健太郎くん！！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Kentaro-kun!!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21896,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　健太郎くん、健太郎くん、健太郎くん……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Kentaro-kun, Kentaro-kun, Kentaro-kun...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21897,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「終わりだ、魔王ッ…………！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's over, Demon King...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21898,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あなた…………ッ、消えろっ…………！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You... disappear...!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21899,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　消えちゃえーーーーーー！！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Vanishhhhhhh!!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21900,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "……………",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "..............."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21901,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「は…………ぁっ…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ha... ah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21902,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "爆発の音に紛れるほど、小さく。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "So small that it was drowned out by the sound of the explosion."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21903,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔王の心臓を、勇者の剣が正確に貫いていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The hero's sword had accurately pierced the Demon King's heart."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21904,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ………………ぁ…………",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah...........ah..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21905,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いた、っ……痛い、な……苦、しぃ、よぅ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It hurts... it really hurts... I'm in so much pain..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21906,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "来水美樹は、息絶えた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Mizusawa Miki passed away."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21907,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………仕留めた、ッ…………",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Got him...!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21908,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　世界は…………これで、救われる……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The world... will be saved by this...!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21909,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "剣を突き出した体勢のまま、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Still in the stance of thrusting his sword out,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21910,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "アリオスはその表情に、徐々に感情を蘇らせていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Arios gradually revived emotion in his expression."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21911,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "姿は、ボロボロだった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "His appearance was battered."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21912,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "度重なる戦闘と魔王の一撃とで深く傷ついていたが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He was deeply wounded from repeated battles and a strike from the Demon King,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21913,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "両目の光は強い。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but the light in both eyes was strong."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21914,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「こ、の……クソ勇者、がっ…………！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yo-you damn hero...!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21915,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　女の子を、殺しておいて……何が救っただっ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You killed a girl... what exactly have you saved...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21916,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「動かないでください、ランス様っ……！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Please don't move, Lord Rance...!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21917,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いたいのいたいの、とんでけー……とんでけー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Pain, pain, fly away... fly away!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21918,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "幾度も回復魔法が繰り返されるが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Recovery magic was repeated many times,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21919,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスの出血は止まらない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but Rance's bleeding would not stop."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21920,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ランス様！　ランス様！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Lord Rance! Lord Rance!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21921,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「必要な、犠牲だったんだ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It was a necessary sacrifice..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21922,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔王は殺さなければならない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The Demon King had to be killed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21923,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔物の脅威から、人類を救う為には……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "To save humanity from the threat of monsters...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21924,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……残念ですが、そうはなりません」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Unfortunately, that's not what will happen.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21925,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"... ?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21926,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「美樹さんが……リトルプリンセスが死んでも、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even if Miki-san... the Little Princess dies,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21927,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　まだまだ人も魔物も死にます」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "people and monsters alike will continue to die.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21928,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だが、もう魔王や魔人の脅威はない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"However, the threat of Demon Kings and demon lords no longer exists."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21929,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　残った魔物も……これから一掃する」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The remaining monsters... will be wiped out from now on.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21930,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そうではありません。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That is not the case."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21931,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　……伝えていないのですね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "...You haven't been told, have you?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21932,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "どこか疲れ果てたような瞳で、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "With eyes that looked somewhat utterly exhausted,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21933,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "クルックーはその人物を見た。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Kurukku looked at that person."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21934,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「まあね、ムーララルー。聞かれなかったんで」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, Muurararu. I wasn't asked about it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21935,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「コーラ？　……何のことだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Kola? ...What do you mean?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21936,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "従者は殊更に、溜息をついて軽く肩を竦める。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The attendant sighed noticeably and shrugged lightly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21937,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔王は、死んでも代替わりするだけですよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The Demon King only gets replaced even if he dies."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21938,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今回は、私の上役が任命する事になるでしょうね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "This time, my superior will probably appoint the next one.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21939,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「上、役…………？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Sup-erior...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21940,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい。三超神プランナー。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes. The Three Super-God Planners."
    }
  ]
}

